Names of Earth Engine Images layers (bands)

ee_name.Rd

Get or set the names of the layers of an Earth Engine Image object.

# S3 method for ee.image.Image
names(x) <- value

# S3 method for ee.image.Image
names(x)

Arguments

x

an EE Image object.
value

a character vector with the same length as x.
